ShortList is a free weekly magazine published in the United Kingdom, which launched on 20 September 2007. The magazine has the biggest circulation of any men's lifestyle magazine in Britain with Joe Mackertich as its editor. Mike Soutar, former editorial director of IPC Media, editor of FHM in the UK and US Maxim, is the Chairman. Ella Dolphin is the CEO.
ShortList Media launched Stylist, a similar magazine for women, in 2009.
